{"tid":1052930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係覺得好孤單呀 無一個真心朋友又無女朋友","createTime":"2019-03-08T15:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T00:18:53.000Z","uid":1249,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8735c71efdf1d05c08cfb98ca1f6903a92840f6d","tid":1052930,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"Facebook 幾百個fds，無一個傾到心事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男仔嘅友誼好脆弱、虛偽。我完全唔夠膽講。<br />\n女仔fds想溝你咪會聽下囉，對你無興趣嘅都唔會當你係&rdquo;fd&rdquo;, 唔怪得d人話男女係無純友誼。<br />\n<br />\n女朋友又無個，有d想追你嘅人又感覺到唔係真心（似想呃蝦條only）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日返工唔知為乜，喺香港份糧都改善唔到生活㗎啦，只係為生存。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好孤單呀𨳒，好撚想喊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5b7e5beef1a1fe5b5367ec9f481dbd671ef37d","tid":1052930,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"可留意兩個post留言既分別"},{"pid":"cbd1f67fc3c82065a4eeb6c806cc33e6f261d478","tid":1052930,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"下 呃蝦條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f07b1c103ad2fe9c2015acfa5686e2a8b97b2e","tid":1052930,"uid":1249,"lik